  "detailed_description": "Bounce is a mini game about getting the ball into the finish point.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPull and rotate the ball to find your way.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Multiple kinds of obstacles.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Diverse level styles.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Explore different approaches to the finish point.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Control your power.Because \"overpower\" doesn't always lead to good results.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe hope you will have a good time playing this game.Enjoy!",
